title: Kim France and Jenn Romolini
itunes:title: Kim France and Jenn Romolini
description: Kim and Jenn dig into their long history - from working together professionally, to collaborating on the "Everything is Fine" podcast as co-hosts. They share their thoughts on exploring opportunities, defining success, and living unapologetically.
